Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,第一是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,是誰 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:40.90,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:54.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥 為什麼 要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,就算被甩了 也不會突然就不喜歡了吧
